# 🌌 MilkyWay

### *The Galactic CTF Orchestrator*

[![Python Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.9%2B-blue.svg)](https://python.org)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-green.svg)](LICENSE)
